2001:db8:2::/64   ::        [{Origin: i} {Communities: 65001:200, 65001:201} {LargeCommunity: [ 65001:200:200]} {MpReach(ipv6-unicast): {Nexthop: ::, NLRIs: [2001:db8:2::/64]}}]
